
User stories for Wen

Add goals, H
As a user, I want to have add goal feature 
so that I can add goals for the day

Use microphone, H 
As a user, I want to be able to  speak instead of typing when I add goals
So that it’s much easier to add a goal

Display app, M
As a user, I want to displayed app each time the phone gets sleep
So that it’s keep reminding me even the phone is sleep

Check off goals, H
As a user, I want to be able to check off my goals
So that I can move to next goal

Don’s display goals that is done for next day, M
As a user, I want to the app do not display the goals that I have done for previous day
So that I can focus on  goals for today

Display the goals that unchecked off for next day, M
As a user, I want to the app be able to display the previous day unchecked goals
So that I can finish it on today







